title: The Deep, Dominant Raptors Keep Rolling Along | The Mismatch (Ep. 333)
description:
A big night for Jamal Murray continues the Denver Nuggets’ hot streak (3:07), the torrid Toronto Raptors add another loss to the Utah Jazz’s disappointing start (14:53), precarious teams face sink-or-swim developments (32:58), and draft prospects look to shine as the college basketball season kicks off (47:55).
Hosts: Chris Vernon, Kevin O’Connor
